\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 26, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104cux1665702759488.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cux1665702759488.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cux1665702759488.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cux1665702759488\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Operation activated by the SAX parser when it encounters character data that it\n    considers to be ignorable whitespace.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104cux1665702759488_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"cux1665702759488__codeblock_nrd_vg4_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation WHITESPACE\n  params\n     string Chars: in\n  endparams\n\nImplement your code here\nend; WHITESPACE operation</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cux1665702759488__section_d4q_vg4_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d571858e53\">Parameters</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Chars</var>—whitepsace characters such as spaces, tabs, carriage returns, and\n        line feeds that the parser considers ignorable.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cux1665702759488__section_hxg_yg4_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d571858e64\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cux1665702759488__p_d137294e1_d137295e1_d137296e1\">If there is no DTD for the XML document being\n        processed, this operation is never called. Instead, whitespace is reported together with\n        other character data by activating the <code class=\"ph codeph\">CHARACTERS</code> operation.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cux1665702759488__p_d137297e1_d137298e1_d137299e1\">If there is a DTD, the parser consideres any\n        whitespace it encounters ignorable and activates the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">WHITESPACE</span>\n        operation, passing it the whitespace characters encountered.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cux1665702759488__p_d137300e1_d137301e1_d137302e1\">For example, the following XML contains a\n        carriage-return and some leading spaces between <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;aaa&gt;</code> and\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;bbb&gt;</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" id=\"cux1665702759488__codeblock_c2b_ks4_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;aaa&gt;\n &lt;bbb&gt;text&lt;/bbb&gt;\n&lt;/aaa&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cux1665702759488__p_d137303e1_d137304e1_d137305e1\">The parameter passed to <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">WHITESPACE</span>\n        will contain the carriage-return and these spaces.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cux1665702759488__p_d137306e1_d137307e1_d137308e1\">Since ignorable whitespace is usually ignored, this\n        operation is normally not implemented.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bry1665702759353.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>CHARACTERS</a><p>Adds the supplied text inside an element.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526632\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526632\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "WHITESPACE Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Operation activated by the SAX parser when it encounters character data that it considers to be ignorable whitespace. Explain this code operation WHITESPACE params string Chars: in endparams Implement your code here end; WHITESPACE operation Copy Parameters Chars —whitepsace characters such as spaces, tabs, carriage returns, and line feeds that the parser considers ignorable. Description If there is no DTD for the XML document being processed, this operation is never called. Instead, whitespace is reported together with other character data by activating the CHARACTERS operation. If there is a DTD, the parser consideres any whitespace it encounters ignorable and activates the WHITESPACE operation, passing it the whitespace characters encountered. For example, the following XML contains a carriage-return and some leading spaces between <aaa> and <bbb> . <aaa> <bbb>text</bbb> </aaa> Copy The parameter passed to WHITESPACE will contain the carriage-return and these spaces. Since ignorable whitespace is usually ignored, this operation is normally not implemented. Related Links CHARACTERS Adds the supplied text inside an element. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}